    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in great shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s super clean and has plenty of life left in it. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so come on by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
